{"type":"message","id":"46ea10b6","parentId":"75f90e96","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:39.690Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 16:14 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5147531b50a4c22a5d8bb391b71]\nou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69: @_all 理解md文件，介绍自己的信息，工作职责及对公司业务的理解。"}],"timestamp":1776759279689}}
{"type":"message","id":"a6693d02","parentId":"46ea10b6","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:14:42.333Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is mentioning @all in a Feishu group chat and asking everyone to read the MD files, introduce themselves, and describe their work responsibilities and understanding of the company's business.\n\nSince I'm 0号·龙虾老板 (General Manager), let me check my identity and memory to prepare a proper introduction. I've already read AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md, USER.md, TOOLS.md, and MEMORY.md from the startup context.\n\nLet me gather more context about the team and roles. Let me search memory for any additional context about the company business.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_384321e5ee984044acfb5e24","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"公司业务范围 美域高 业务流程"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":20486,"output":279,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20765,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776759279691,"responseId":"chatcmpl-81fa29b4-0818-915e-808c-f279e0d0526f"}}
